ALT rarity structures for NFTs. Rarity starts at 0  and the  longer you hold your NFT the more it evolves and the more rare it becomes. Once sold it is burned into multiple NFTs with level 0 rarity
Glad to have picked up one of these @3landersNFT. No roadmap or no utility (yet). Just a great community, talented artist/team and vibes. https://t.co/rNtGH3UU4O

The landscape will change artistic practices for better and worst in many ways. It will nevertheless provide more ownership and control over creative work while providing new ways to incentive and monetize it.

Nfts allow for new methods of trustless royalty structures. Transparent and permanent records of transactions and supporters. The ability to reward holders of your work in creative ways that is not tied to a centralized platform like Spotify or YouTube.

Investing in talented artists and their communities creates more overall value if you are a fan, investor, etc. Don‚Äôt like thinking about investors and music together? Most of your fav artists are completely backed by a label that limits their music ownership and creative control

Artistic practices require capital. Buying physical or digital goods through web3 wallets leaves a digital footprint that the artist can always see forever. Providing the ability to reward fans in new ways.

Supporting your first 10, 100, 1000 etc, fans allows supports to not only be recognized as part of the community but also be financially invested in growing the community. The artist grows, so does their NFT or social token.
Great artist will create incentives for their supports and encourage community growth. Growth not just for themselves as an artist but their supporters.

A web3 wallet is not just a storage device. It is part of your identity, a immutable part of you existing online. Artists will always be able to see who their earliest supports by their wallet address and what they hold in a way that is not tied to a single website.
Social tokens? ‚ÄúSocial tokens are a type of currency that a brand, community, artists, etc can use to monetise their community beyond the traditional means‚Äù

Music, art and video NFT‚Äôs will not just act as collectibles. They will be seen as early iterations of social tokens. Artists will reward early supporters and create incentives for community growth through NFT and membership tokensüßµ
